Settings window (opened by systray)
[] #include <LibGUI/SettingsWindow.h>
[] These preferences should be remembered using LibConfig Config::write and Config::read
[] Set time for displaying keys using SpinBox
[] Set font, font size, font color using FontPicker
[] Set background color and opacity using ColorPicker and Slider
[] Select Show Modifiers && Combine keys using CheckBox and ComboBox
[] Compress repeat key presses after N presses using SpinBox

System Tray
[] #include <LibGUI/Tray.h>
